# Fraud rule scoring: weighted sum thresholded.
*score(flags as Vec of i64, weights as Vec of i64, n as i64, threshold as i64) returns i64
    s is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        s is s + flags.get(i) * weights.get(i)
        i is i + 1
    if s >= threshold
        return 1
    0

*main
    f is vec()
    f.push(1)
    f.push(0)
    f.push(1)
    f.push(1)
    w is vec()
    w.push(30)
    w.push(20)
    w.push(50)
    w.push(40)
    log score(f, w, 4, 100)
